    "description":  "A project management collaboration app helps teams manage tasks, timelines, and resources efficiently. However, users face challenges in coordinating across different teams and time zones, leading to miscommunications and project delays. The company seeks to enhance collaboration features to streamline communications, improve task visibility, and ensure project milestones are met. Users need to manage tasks, share documents, track project progress, and communicate seamlessly across devices. The design goal is to create a mobile app interface that enhances collaboration and communication within multi-stakeholder projects. The app must integrate with existing tools like calendars and file storage services, and handle edge cases such as offline access and role-based permissions. The design must also consider scalability to accommodate growing teams and project complexities.",
    "task_requirements":  "Design the following screens:\n\n1ГЇВёВЏГўВѓВЈ Project Dashboard\nThis screen provides an overview of all active projects.\nInclude:\nГўВЂВў list of projects with status indicators\nГўВЂВў filters for project stages and deadlines\nГўВЂВў quick access to recent activities and updates\nГўВЂВў prominent \u0027Create New Project\u0027 button\n\n2ГЇВёВЏГўВѓВЈ Task Management Screen\nThis screen allows users to manage and assign tasks.\nInclude:\nГўВЂВў task list with priority and status labels\nГўВЂВў assignment feature to allocate tasks to team members\nГўВЂВў deadline setting options\nГўВЂВў task dependencies visualization\n\n3ГЇВёВЏГўВѓВЈ Document Collaboration Screen\nThis screen supports document sharing and version control.\nInclude:\nГўВЂВў document upload and sharing capabilities\nГўВЂВў version history with timestamp\nГўВЂВў real-time editing indicators\nГўВЂВў comments and feedback sections\n\n4ГЇВёВЏГўВѓВЈ Team Communication Screen\nThis screen facilitates team communication and updates.\nInclude:\nГўВЂВў chat interface for project-specific discussions\nГўВЂВў notifications for mentions and updates\nГўВЂВў integration with calendar for scheduling meetings\nГўВЂВў options for voice and video calls\n\n5ГЇВёВЏГўВѓВЈ User Roles and Permissions Screen\nThis screen manages roles and permissions for team members.\nInclude:\nГўВЂВў role assignment and customization\nГўВЂВў permission settings for different user roles\nГўВЂВў audit logs for changes in roles\nГўВЂВў interface for adding or removing team members",
